comments: Jackson Jr. (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with LaVine (CHI) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.

Markkanen (CHI) and Jackson Jr. (MEM) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
